msgstr ""
"A very colourful planet appears in the distance. As you get closer, you see that large parts "
"of its surface are decorated with elaborate geometric patterns. But there are also a few "
"undecorated areas, completely white. You land in one of these white spots. \n"
"\n"
"**You**: Hello, is anyone here? \n"
"\n"
"The planet's surface resembles a perfect sphere. There's a smooth horizon in every "
"direction. But there's no one to be seen. You are about to turn back when you notice "
"something. \n"
